::Prowl::

Walking out of the torture chamber, Prowl recieves Shocker's transmission. He 
swears silently. A battle ouside the Alliance base was not good.

"No! Retreat right now. We'll get out fine," he replies, forming the message 
and sending it instead of saying the words, "With a battle outside, we're not 
going to have good chances of escape."
